('37147', '5', 'b'Add 6 tablespoons of the olive dressing and toss gently.''),
('37147', '6', 'b'Spread the cut sides of the rolls or baguette pieces with the remaining olive dressing. On the bottom halves of the rolls or baguette pieces, arrange the snow peas, followed by the red onion slices, the tomatoes, tuna and sliced eggs. Close the tuna sandwiches and serve.''),
